title: Where the Magic Happens
description: Gwen takes the team to a dimension of magic, where their only hope of survival rests with her old foe Charmcaster.

title: Inside Man
description: Ben and company rescue Tyler, a runaway prisoner of the DNAliens while trying to stop them from completing the Jump Gate.

title: Everybody Talks About the Weather
description: Gwen discovers Grandpa Max's Plumbers Badge emits a map showing the location of other Plumbers. Ben, Gwen and Kevin follow the map to nearby town and run into a heatblast. He helps the heroes discover that DNAliens have taken over the town and have erected a tower to control the weather. Ben must develop leadership skills to help a young hero save his hometown.

title: The Perfect Girlfriend
description: When Ben finds himself in an intense battle against Ssserpent, Julie steps in and helps him defeat the slimy brute.

title: Pet Project
description: Ben and company must rescue the shape-shifting, dog-like alien, Ship, from the Forever Knights.

title: Ultimate Aggregor
description: Aggregor's ultimate plan is revealed, and it's already too late to stop him!

title: Alone Together
description: Ben is transported to a distant planet alongside a Highbreed Commander. They must work together to get off the planet alive.

title: Simple
description: When Ben arrives on a distant planet to try and help broker peace between warring factions, he ends up transforming into a new alien named Lodestar.

title: Vengeance of Vilgax Part 2
description: In the conclusion of this epic battle, Vilgax battles an array of Aliens and is close to ending Ben forever. But Diamondhead has different plans.

title: Basic Training
description: Ben and the crew are forced to go through basic training at the Plumber's Academy. And you can just imagine how well that goes.

title: Simian Says
description: An evil Highbreed queen takes over the Arachnachimp's home planet by attaching herself to a crime lord named Mizaru.

title: Solitary Alignment
description: Azmuth reveals how old George first got the sword and defeated Dagon, and the crew travels to the Middle Ages to learn the truth.

title: Game Over
description: When Ben, as Upgrade, and Gwen get zapped into a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben soon has to deal with Gwen's superior gaming skills, while he also tries to impress his video icon in the game.

title: The Enemy of My Enemy
description: Argit infiltrates the Plumber's Academy with a plan to help the Vreedle Brothers do the last thing anyone would expect.

title: The Creature from Beyond
description: The Forever Knights accidentally unleash an evil force! And at a Bellwood retirement home, a retired Forever Knight suddenly gets a very bad feeling.

title: Absolute Power Part 1
description: Ben is infuriated when Gwen asks Darkstar for his help defeating the team's deadliest, and most unlikely foe of all.

title: Map of Infinity
description: Ben and his team travel to a bizarre half-frozen, half molten planet to prevent Aggregor from obtaining a priceless map.

title: Prisoner #775 Is Missing
description: When old George enters Area 51 and makes the entire base disappear, Ben and the crew learn that a mysterious Prisoner 775 may be behind it all.

title: Con of Rath
description: Ben is on a special mission when the Omnitrix malfunctions and turns him into an Appoplexian named Rath who wants to fight anything that breaths.

title: The Flame Keepers' Circle
description: A fanatical group of whackos have taken to worshiping Vilgax of all people or aliens! And guess who has joined them, Julie!

title: Fame
description: Ben's secret identity is revealed to the world, and an alien refugee is about to detonate a nuclear bomb.

title: Catch a Falling Star
description: Movie starlet Jennifer Nocturne springs the evil Captain Nemesis out of jail and the two escape and soon, Ben and Gwen are hot on their trail.

title: Darkstar Rising
description: Ben and co. must uncover the truth of a mysterious new villain, Darkstar.

title: Escape from Aggregor
description: Five aliens from another galaxy attempt to escape from their mysterious captor.

title: Max Out
description: Gwen's older brother, Ken, disappears and she gets Ben and Kevin to help her track him down. Their investigation leads them to find not only Ken but also another long-missing relative and a startling secret of the DNAliens. This discovery comes at a high cost as Ben is left with greater responsibilities than ever before.

title: The Widening Gyre
description: After a giant garbage-like creature appears drags a boat down into the ocean, Ben and the crew investigate the Pacific Garbage Vortex.

title: Inspector #13
description: A mysterious Techadon Master visits Earth, looking for the Ultimatrix. And he turns out to be more dangerous than any Techadon ever imagined.

title: The Eggman Cometh
description: When vicious dragons invade Bellwood, it's up to Ben and an all-new alien named Jury Rigg to battle the flying demons and return the peace.

title: The Transmogrification of Eunice
description: The team discovers a strange alien girl with no memory but Sunder has been hired to capture her!

title: The Ultimate Sacrifice
description: Ben is suddenly NOT Ben and it's an all-out revolt as the Aliens inside Ben's Ultimatrix demand their freedom.

title: It's Not Easy Being Gwen
description: You think it's easy being Gwen? Well you'll have second thoughts after you check out a typical day in the not-so-typical life of Gwen Tennyson.

title: Time Heals
description: Gwen travels back in time to prevent the accident that turned Kevin into a monster from ever happening. But she ends up altering history forever.

title: Ben 10,000 Returns
description: Eon is back and it's up to an older and wiser Ben from the future to help the crew defeat him using the Hands of Armageddon to win the battle.

title: Ben 10 Returns Part 1
description: Ben Tennyson is a normal teenager who has put away his toys including the Omnitrix that gave him his powers. Ben's life take a turn when he is attacked by an alien and discovers Grandpa Max is missing. To find his grandpa, Ben teams up with his cousin, Gwen, his grandpa's partner, Magister, and even his former nemesis, Kevin 11. When they discover the Forever Knights (a secret organization that deals in illegal alien technology) and DNAliens (the Highbreeds henchmen) are trading dangerous weapons, Ben decides to once again put on the Omnitrix and quickly learns he can now transform into ten new aliens.

title: If All Else Fails
description: A hibernating Highbreed officer awakens and triggers a device designed to destroy the planet. Now Ben must figure out a way to stop him.

title: Birds of a Feather
description: Ben and company help the prince of the arachna-chimps, Simian, return to power.

title: Voided
description: Ben goes into the Null Void to aid the Plumber's Helpers defeat D'Void.

title: Duped
description: Under pressure from his newfound fame, Ben comes up with a plan to be at more than one place at a time.

title: Perplexahedron
description: Ben, Kevin and Gwen race Aggregor through a mysterious artificial planetoid designed to destroy anyone who enters.

title: The Purge
description: The Forever Knights factions have been united into one and an all-out war against the aliens on Earth erupts.

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: The Enemy of My Frenemy
description: Gwen hopes to rescue Charmcaster. When she asks Hex to join her, he refuses saying he won't join a suicide mission.

title: In Charm's Way
description: Kevin is charmed by a beautiful girl and finds himself under her spell (literally) as Charmcaster has returned and is forcing Kevin to do her biding.

title: Vengeance of Vilgax Part 1
description: Armed with the power of 10 Alien Champions, Vilgax sets his sites on Earth. And the only hero standing in his way Is Ben Tennyson.

title: Grounded
description: Ben and Gwen manage to get grounded, leaving Kevin alone to fight the DNAliens.

title: The Final Battle Part 1
description: Albedo Ben has stolen the Ultimatrix from Azmuth and has used it to kidnap Gwen and Kevin. So Ben goes to face Albedo Ben and rescue his friends.

title: Moonstruck
description: Grandpa Max reveals the story of how he met Verdona and how he eventually was recruited to become a Plumber.

title: Reflected Glory
description: JT and Cash get in over their heads when they take credit for Ben's heroic acts.

title: Nor Iron Bars a Cage
description: To settle an old score, Kevin voluntarily returns to the Null Void prison he once escaped.

title: Ghost Town
description: Vilgax visits Ghostfreak in prison and gets more than he bargained for when Ghostfreak begins possessing the citizens of Vilgaxia.

title: Night of the Living Nightmare
description: Albedo is desperate to get his hands on the Ultimatrix and he goes to extreme measures to get it. Once he has invaded Ben's mind, all bets are off.

title: Benwolf
description: In New Mexico, Max stops to visit an old friend, who's a Navajo Chief. Suddenly, a powerful storm comes out of nowhere. And behind bolts of purple lightning, a Navajo werewolf appears. As Ben battles the werewolf, he appears to be bitten and turns into Benwolf.

title: The Forge of Creation
description: Professor Paradox holds the key to stopping Aggregor from tapping into the limitless power of Alien X.

title: Trade-Off!
description: Darkstar, convinces Kevin to join him in a quest for an ancient artifact with the ability to help them both escape their current degenerate states.

title: Andreas' Fault
description: The team discovers that alien con-man Argit has somehow become the leader of the Forever Knights.

title: Super Alien Hero Buddy Adventures
description: Ben discovers his alien heroes have been ripped off by a lame cartoon and he is not happy. So he sets out to make things right.

title: The Final Battle Part 2
description: A defeated Ben gives up the Omnitrix to save himself and his friends. Powerless, he boards Vilgax's ship for their final battle!

title: Deep
description: Ben, Kevin, and Gwen journey to the center of an all-water planet in an attempt to finally of capture Aggregor.

title: Girl Trouble
description: Gwen's cousin, Sunny, pays a visit but she's more than meets the eye!

title: Hero Time
description: A starstruck Ben dates a beautiful young movie actress, while his childhood hero makes a comeback.

title: X Equals Ben Plus 2
description: The Incursians blame Earth for the kidnapping of Emperor Milleus' daughter, Attea. Raff, the Emperor's right-hand man, recruits Kevin to help them recover Attea before the Emperor uses the Conquest Ray to destroy the Earth. Ben transforms into Alien X but soon discovers his powers are too great to control. Ben must gain control over Alien X before Emperor Milleus can use the Conquest Ray to blow up Earth.

title: Be-Knighted
description: The Forever Knights have secured an alien weapon that will help them kill a dragon they have held captive for centuries. After the dragon escapes, they must ask Ben for help in recapturing it. Ben agrees to help but soon discovers the real identity of the dragon along with its ulterior motive for wanting to return to the Forever Knights. Ben must use his head, not just his brawn, in finding a peaceful solution to the impending fight between the dragon and the knights.

title: Fool's Gold
description: When an alien named Orb asks for help finding his missing friend, Decka, Ben, Gwen and Kevin are surprised to learn just how valuable a friend he is.

title: Absolute Power Part 2
description: It's Ben and company's last stand against a foe they can't bring themselves to fight!

title: The Ultimate Enemy Part 2
description: Vilgax re-emerges in his most powerful form ever! Can Ben stop him and save the universe?

title: The Gauntlet
description: After years of Ben being picked on by the school bullies Cash and JT, Ben stands up for himself and embarrasses both of them in front of a group of peers. An upset Cash later retaliates by pushing Kevin's GTO down a hill where a robot hand pops out of the trunk after it hits a tree. Cash and JT steal off with the glove only to have the glove possess Cash, granting him the power to get revenge on Ben.

title: Revenge of the Swarm
description: When Julie is kidnapped, Ben blames Elena who swears she had nothing to do with it. But the nanochips in her lab point to the truth.

title: Greetings from Techadon
description: A mysterious object crashes in the center of Bellwood, unleashing Techadon robots with one thing on their mind, destroying Ben!

title: Couples Retreat
description: After Darkstar opens the Door to Anywhere, Charmcaster comes through and the two team up to give Ben, Gwen and Kevin the fight of a lifetime.

title: The Beginning of the End
description: As the final battle between the Forever Knights and Dagon's Esoterica heats up, Ben finds himself caught in the middle of an intergalactic showdown.

title: Inferno
description: Ben, Gwen and Kevin investigate the explosion of a mysterious machine, unleashing hundreds of rock eating aliens. Not good news for Kevin!

title: Ben 10 Returns Part 2
description: After defeating the Forever Knights, Ben, Gwen and Kevin follow a lead that takes them to a secret base in the desert. There they hope to find their missing Grandpa but instead find a spaceship with a giant cannon. The Highbreed intend to use it to destroy a nearby city. The trio of heroes is able to stop the ship and afterward they decide to team up for good in order find the missing Grandpa Max and unveil the secret alien plot of the Highbreed.

title: The Mother of All Vreedles
description: Ma Vreedle returns to Earth with a cloning machine and a plan to unleash 300 billion Pretty Boy Vreedles on the planet.

title: Single Handed
description: A bounty hunter is hot on Ben, but when he gets his chance to remove the Omnitrix from Ben's wrist, he sends Ben deep into the Null Void!

title: Plumber's Helpers
description: Manny and Helen are a rogue team of young plumbers trying to track down aliens. When they mistake Ben and his team for dangerous aliens, they end up kidnapping Kevin. Ben and Gwen need to track them down.

title: Viktor: The Spoils
description: The return of the evil Dr. Viktor!

title: The Ultimate Enemy Part 1
description: Dagon is getting closer and closer to entering our dimension thanks to an old foe.

title: The Secret of Chromastone
description: Ben meets up with Tetrax but is caught off guard when Tetrax demands that he give him Chromastone. Before Ben has a chance to explain, Tetrax attacks.

title: Double or Nothing
description: Albedo, aka Negative Ben, returns as the star big stage production about Ben Tennyson's life. Sure he needs the money, but what is he really up to?

title: Fused
description: Ben is trapped in the form of his newest transformation, a form Aggregor intends to destroy.

title: War of the Worlds Part 1
description: Ben must recruit the other Plumber's kids to help stop the Highbreed invasion of Earth.

title: Video Games
description: Ben's celebrity lands him a starring role in his own video game.

title: Save the Last Dance
description: Ben grows worried as he slowly starts to lose control of the Omnitrix.

title: A Knight to Remember
description: Vilgax gets a hold of Old George's sword, and tries to gain Dagon's power. Big mistake! And Ben discovers two new alien heroes: Fasttrack and Eatle.

title: Busy Box
description: Kevin, Ben, and Gwen find a curious box that has the ability to turn into a robot version of whatever it sees. All is well till the Vreedles show up.

title: Pier Pressure
description: After Julie Yamamoto wins a tennis match, Ben gets up the nerve to take her out on a date to the nearby Pier. Their first date is ruined as Ship, a small piece of an alien pilot, begins to take over the carnival rides and attacks Ben. Ben is able to withstand the attacks only to have Ship kidnap Julie! Ben runs the risk of exposing his secret to Julie as he is forced to follow Ship and find out why Ship insists on fighting him.

title: All That Glitters
description: Grandpa Max left a message for Ben instructing him to gather a team of heroes. Ben finds a powerful new ally named Mike Morningstar but the addition of Mike to the team tests the relationships of Ben, Gwen and Kevin. Ben learns the importance of using judgment as a leader when our group of heroes finds the truth behind a series of attacks by Zombie Girls.

title: Too Hot to Handle
description: A radioactive alien menace tricks Kevin into freeing him from his containment suit.

title: Kevin's Big Score
description: Ben and Gwen are finally starting to trust Kevin when Kevin steals the Rustbucket and tries to swap it for some alien tech from Argit! Argit then steals the Rustbucket from Kevin and runs away. Ben and Gwen must learn to trust a flawed teammate as they help Kevin claim the important alien tech he is desperately after and face off with one of Ben's old foes, Vulkanus.

title: Undercover
description: Ben and company must rescue Cooper, a kid genius, from the DNAliens who are forcing him to help build a mysterious arch.

title: Primus
description: In the middle of fighting a Techadon robot, Ben, Kevin, and Gwen are unexpectedly transported by the Omnitrix to an alien planet named Primus.

title: Unearthed
description: Ben and company need to return a baby monster to its parents before the DNAliens find it.

title: Above and Beyond
description: The Plumber's Helpers are called upon by Grandpa Max to rescue him from an abandoned space station where he is being attacked by - Ben!

title: War of the Worlds Part 2
description: Ben and his team travel to the Highbreed home world to stop them once and for all.

title: The Big Story
description: When a mysterious meteor shower leaves behind an evil alien plant species, Ben 10 super-fan Jimmy steps up to save the day.

title: Good Copy, Bad Copy
description: An alien doppelganger impersonates Ben and is out to destroy him with the power of his own Omnitrix.

title: What Are Little Girls Made Of?
description: Ben and Gwen learn Max's wife, Verdona, is an alien and Gwen's magic is actually inherited alien power from their grandma. After learning the truth, Gwen is forced to choose between keeping her life as she knows it and sacrificing all that she has to become a being of great power.

title: Vendetta
description: Kevin finds his house ransacked and enlists Ben and Gwen's help to find out who did it and why. They soon cross paths with a deadly criminal.

title: Paradox
description: A time experiment in the 1950's rips a bizarre monster from the past that threatens the future of Ben's time. It's a race against time as Ben, Gwen and Kevin team up with Paradox, a time-traveling hero, to face off against the unstoppable creature.

title: Hit 'Em Where They Live
description: Now that Ben's secret identity is out in the open, his old enemies team up to attack his family.

title: Monster Weather
description: Max takes the kids to a drought stricken Chicago to see his favorite golden oldie band perform at a huge music festival. Once there, our heroes cross paths with a deranged weatherman.

title: The Eye of the Beholder
description: Ship's former owner, Baz-L, has been captured on a distant planet while stealing gems and Ben, Julie and the crew set out to save him.

title: Don't Fear the Repo
description: Repo men, Octagon and Rhomboid Vreedle, have been hired to return Ship to the Upgrade who spawned him. But Ben, Kevin and Gwen have different plans.
